<i>adverb</i>: 외로이 [외로이/웨로이], 외따로 [외따로/웨따로], 쓸쓸히 [쓸쓸히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>외로이 [외로이/웨로이]</dt><br>
<dd>lonelily; solitarily</dd><br>
<dd>혼자가 되거나 의지할 데가 없어서 쓸쓸하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a lonesome manner because one is alone or has nobody to depend on.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>외따로 [외따로/웨따로]</dt><br>
<dd>solitarily</dd><br>
<dd>혼자 따로.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of being alone.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>쓸쓸히 [쓸쓸히]</dt><br>
<dd>lonesomely; solitarily</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 외롭고 허전하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of feeling lonely and empty.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>